Enemy: NPCs that want to hurt you
Characters: NPCs that (usually) don't want to hurt you
Mechanics: devices, props, and appliances that help you progress (buttons, levers, pushable boxes, etc)
Hazards: devices, props, and appliances that harm you
Pickups: items you can collect
Weapons/Tools: items that you can collect and equip
Easter Eggs: stuff that serve zero gameplay purpose whatsoever and are only there to look cool or for lore.
